# iOS Build Config

## Xcode Sync Groups

This project uses Xcode file system synchronized groups for `Portent/` and `portentTests/`.

- ✅ Create new Swift files, asset catalogs, and test files directly under `apps/ios/Portent/` or `apps/ios/portentTests/`
- ✅ Xcode will include them automatically — no project file edits needed
- ❌ Do not add `PBXFileReference` or `PBXBuildFile` entries for source or asset files
- ❌ Do not modify `project.pbxproj` just to register new files

## When to Edit project.pbxproj

Only update `Portent.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj` for actual project configuration:

- Build settings (e.g. `INFOPLIST_FILE`, deployment target)
- Package dependencies
- Signing and target configuration
- Version/build number (per repo bump workflow)

If you are only adding files under `Portent/` or `portentTests/`, do not touch `project.pbxproj`.
